Công ty B2B', '科技初创公司\\nSaaS平台\\n服务提供商\\n企业对企业公司', '科技初創公司\\nSaaS平台\\n服務提供商\\n企業對企業公司', 'Responsive Design & UX - Beautiful, fast interfaces that convert on desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.\nHigh-Speed Performance - Optimized loading times, Core Web Vitals, and zero technical debt.\nSEO Optimization - Built-in structured data, fast rendering, and conversion-friendly page architecture.\nIntegration Support - Seamless connections to your CRM, email, analytics, and payment systems.', 'Thiết kế Phản hồi & UX\\nHiệu suất Tốc độ cao\\nTối ưu hóa SEO\\nHỗ trợ Tích hợp\\nBảo trì Hàng tháng', '响应式设计和用户体验\\n高速性能\\nSEO优化\\n集成支持\\n每月维护', '響應式設計和用戶體驗\\n高速性能\\nSEO優化\\n集成支持\\n每月維護', 4, true, true, '2026-03-17T07:17:36.015Z', '2026-03-17T07:17:36.015Z');
