ertise, and cultural understanding tailored to Chinese consumer behavior.', 'Global Companies\\nExport Businesses\\nCross-border Sellers\\nAmbitious Brands', 'Công ty Toàn cầu\\nDoanh nghiệp Xuất khẩu\\nNhà bán Xuyên biên giới\\nThương hiệu Tham vọng', '全球公司\\n出口企业\\n跨境卖家\\n雄心勃勃的品牌', '全球公司\\n出口企業\\n跨境賣家\\n雄心勃勃的品牌', 'Market Entry Strategy - In-depth analysis and go-to-market planning for Chinese e-commerce platforms.\nLocal Partnership Setup - Connecting you with trusted logistics, payment, and compliance partners in China.\nCultural Localization - Adapt your brand messaging, visuals, and operations for Chinese consumers.\nGovernment Compliance - Navigate licensing, tax requirements, and regulatory frameworks.', 'Chiến lược Vào thị trường\\nThiết lập Quan hệ Đối tác Địa phương\\nBản địa hóa Văn hóa\\nTích hợp Thanh toán\\nTuân thủ Chính phủ', '市场进入战略\\n本地合作伙伴建立\\n文化本地化\\n支付集成\\n政府合规', '市場進入戰略\\n本地合作夥伴建立\\n文化本地化\\n支付集成\\n政府合規', 7, true, true, '2026-03-17T07:17:36.110Z', '2026-03-17T07:17:36.110Z');
